tspan.tspan: You can imagine, as Owl often would,
the invisible threads strung in between
vibrating info among the atoms
from quarks to stars and parts as yet unseen.
Now binding strings to common ends will find
a superimposition of all things
in harmonies and destructive pulses
confined within a single, complex ring.
And Owl - high amplitude but narrow width -
in contempt regards wideband monolith.
Reluctantly absorbed he falls in black
beside whistling winds and whipping cloaks,
subjecting self to governing patterns
until such time he can amble backward
and spy the ordered cancer in the noise
where cells of automata join to die -
decay to static, inward inaction.
Potential gets sapped by energy well,
increasing band-gap leaves only a fall
then wandering by torchlight through tomb halls.
Trembling they shiver as blank silhouettes,
as simple shimmers to be extinguished
were they without warm-lit relief - behold:
Golden figures from olden storied tales,
Crowns bejeweled, halos surround, vacant-faced
looking from monied hands to muddied lands,
they lift their skinny fists like antennas
and towers rise to meet them in the stars
where the left hand stops the sun in its bout
and the right holds the planet to their mouth.
